Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.63,0:00:08.07,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, I'll do as Dad said.\NI'll enter the Tournament of the Gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.30,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to become Bilicus's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:14.28,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:17.24,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I could be with you then, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.51,0:00:18.67,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.15,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.06,0:00:35.86,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Tournament of the Gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:43.00,Anime Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Tournament of the Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:43.00,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(336,445)}Blue Storm Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.24,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:26.81,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep staring, they'll think\Nyou're from the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.61,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Selena, I'm not a child anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:32.98,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.29,0:01:34.95,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:36.95,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:49.96,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, the entrant is Sid, and\Nhis partner is Selena, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.27,0:01:50.97,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:55.24,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you two are lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:59.77,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Selena is like my older sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:03.45,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're all signed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.92,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a pre-victory celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:08.69,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overhasty, Selena!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.66,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.83,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Your state of mind is important in\Nthis kind of thing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:19.29,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you don't win, Azuki will\Nhave to marry Bilicus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.20,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have no choice but to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:27.11,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win, then I can be with Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:29.78,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my promise to Azuki's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.68,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But Azuki is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:33.01,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:36.21,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.92,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be in the Tournament\Nof the Gods too, Sid?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.63,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.25,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight hard, okay?\NI'll be rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:48.73,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:52.03,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the weakest one even at\Nthe Mizuhara Dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:56.40,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never get through even the\Nfirst round of the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.07,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.68,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid will make it through\Nall the rounds and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:06.14,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall look forward to fighting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:09.42,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miss, let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:13.88,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that Sid has entered the\NTournament, he is our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:18.66,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you, Sid.\NYou have to win, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:24.03,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try not to lose in a fashion that will\Ndishonor the name of the Mizuhara Dojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:34.81,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go ahead with the\Npre-victory celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.07,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.55,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely win, Azuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.81,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:45.85,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you drank so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.32,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Selena,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.29,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,why are you taking you're top off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.26,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:59.13,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.90,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,And a young one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:03.50,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.50,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I also know that you're still a virgin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:13.51,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in trouble if you underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.57,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been like a mother to you\Nfor a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.19,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So be even more understanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.56,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:21.52,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:26.56,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you a man, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:30.52,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as your father made me a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.93,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My father did?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:35.07,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I loved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:38.06,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked him to make love to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:42.94,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But that happened after your mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.98,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, even though I loved him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:47.14,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Selena...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:48.97,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.05,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:55.89,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for Azuki too, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:56.65,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:05:00.22,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki is probably still a virgin too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.50,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:06.70,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time for a girl is a very\Npainful thing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:11.77,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,And if her partner is a virgin who doesn't\Nknow his left from his right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:16.47,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you feel bad if her important\Nfirst time was like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:22.58,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems you're not saying\N"no" down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.65,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you too, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:30.16,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.72,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:35.36,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:46.87,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:03.61,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you take them off for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:14.93,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. Slowly, as if to highlight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:19.04,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, so that you don't make\Nyour partner nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.27,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can make them anticipate it,\Neven better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:44.83,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, hold your partner to\Ntake away their anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:50.79,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let your partner know\N"my body is excited."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:53.13,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Slide your body against theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.94,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.88,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's so soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.13,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:34.31,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! That hurts, Sid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.05,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.25,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You're using too much force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:46.88,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand, girls are very delicate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.03,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Gently, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.47,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You look for where your partner\Nreacts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.87,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.10,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.81,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:49.42,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you let it out,\Nit's already healthy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:49.54,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! I'm your waitress, Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.71,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, have a menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.31,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.22,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, I'll treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:59.05,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then a tofu-cake for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.72,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be participating\Nin the tournament, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:07.60,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the partner of a\Nparticipant last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.96,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But we lost a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:14.73,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've had to work at this\Nbar for free since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.44,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's only until this year's\Ntournament is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.20,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be allowed to return to\Nmy hometown soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.70,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:34.09,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.06,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is the Champion, Krank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:40.72,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can defy the Champion in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.86,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.40,0:11:46.66,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being called, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.46,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:58.81,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka, you're as cute today as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:03.48,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So console my "son" as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:05.39,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.30,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:19.83,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sid. He's the Champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:23.30,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you could\Nbeat him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.03,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.04,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:07.44,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the level-up dungeon,\NLagunard Labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:10.75,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.12,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to do the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.62,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:16.69,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, my goal is to\Nwin the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.16,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use dying during training.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.06,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:51.12,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband who died in the\Ntournament rests in this grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:59.83,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return my husband's sword to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:07.97,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this girl before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.51,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:16.91,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Please guard your life, so that the one\Nwho loves you won't suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:21.46,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The jewel on Kara's forehead is\Nsupposed to be very valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:26.33,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Moutaijin of the Thieves' Guild\Nput out a reward for Kara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.32,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,She hides in the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:50.38,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's time for the first round.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:54.45,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Selena, will I really be able to win?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:01.43,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right.\NHave some confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.79,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still time before the battle, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.33,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:19.38,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go get something\Nto drink, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.18,0:15:23.65,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have drinks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.58,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid. She was being considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.49,0:15:30.51,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.46,0:15:38.62,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a victory charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.70,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Now I'll definitely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:52.71,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Introducing the young warrior, Sid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:01.68,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So hurry up and screw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:05.85,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I know what happens to\Nthe loser's partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:12.83,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're scared, because you've\Nnever had a girl before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:15.33,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I have so had one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.33,0:17:17.30,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you get started?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.70,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I'd feel anything with\Nyour pathetic technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.54,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure you feel something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:34.75,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't feel good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.23,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.34,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.01,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.45,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in a\Nplace like this, Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:21.86,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you win in the first round,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.86,0:18:24.77,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and I decided I couldn't sit there\Nand chance losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:28.33,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to train in\Nthis labyrinth too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:32.67,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But you should have been able to\Nkill that monster easily, Azuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:35.04,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.41,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times\NI killed the monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:40.45,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,it kept coming after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.05,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought about it until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.89,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time I realized my\Nopponent is a living creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.72,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and all of a sudden I got scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:51.02,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:54.79,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever been scared\Nwhen you fought, Sid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:56.93,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.23,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to become stronger
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.20,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,so that I can protect those\Nthat are important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.10,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.57,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:09.10,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, your strength is different than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:15.11,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:31.09,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:50.18,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, you've come to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.35,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.81,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sid. You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.89,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kuraiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.89,0:20:03.10,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell into a trap meant to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.06,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.44,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one on that wanted poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.54,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:13.30,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Kara fear people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:18.90,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you fell in the trap\Nmeant for me, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:22.58,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you tried to save Chururu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:33.03,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it's been discovered that\NI'm hiding in the labyrinth,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:36.19,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and traps have been set\Nall over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.47,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the thieves have posted\Na reward for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:43.44,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:49.11,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The humans are after the jewels\Nin our foreheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:53.24,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Kara can't live\Nwithout their jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.55,0:20:54.75,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.75,0:20:58.91,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,To kill such kind people just for jewels...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:04.55,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,To humans, we Kara are just\Nanother type of monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.89,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:10.85,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters attack people, but you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:13.56,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my treasured friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:16.80,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.41,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:23.57,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been just Chururu and me for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.88,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.69,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, did you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:36.65,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When Kara are reborn, they become\Neither an angel or a devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.89,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I want to become an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.03,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:49.13,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:51.99,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, I'll come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.14,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A Kara in the labyrinth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.45,0:22:02.71,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the customers were saying\Nthat one was caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.31,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be Kuraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:13.02,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The red jewel on your forehead means\Nyou're still a virgin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:15.53,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, moi knows that the one that\Nknows men, the blue stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.50,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,is the one that brings the higher prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:21.00,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like moi's going to have moi some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:38.29,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're a little late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.66,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just handed the Kara girl over to the\NMoutaijin a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:43.71,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:07.88,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, I don't even know how many\Ntimes I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.05,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the orders of the Moutaijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.85,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The more she does it with men,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:13.85,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,the more the jewel on her forehead shines,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:15.82,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,and the more the price goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:17.55,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.03,0:23:24.59,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuraiya, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:27.67,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:33.20,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my cute pee-ons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:40.91,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,But weaklings who lose to one little\Nboy aren't MY pee-ons.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:48.52,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You! How dare you do such horrible\Nthings to Kuraiya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:52.48,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you think you're going to\Nlast against moi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.89,0:23:54.05,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:56.96,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:01.40,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,A little sword attack just\Nwill not work on moi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:02.63,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.74,0:24:09.14,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That you think to defy moi with\Nonly your puny strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.14,0:24:11.63,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! That's why moi hates kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.35,0:24:19.41,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.45,0:24:22.12,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:26.03,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.26,0:24:28.23,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.73,0:24:30.06,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Kara, for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:32.62,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,you're risking your life in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.23,0:24:35.79,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My only friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.44,0:24:40.60,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.65,0:24:52.91,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of this jewel, I'II...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.73,0:25:05.49,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.20,0:25:07.76,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuraiya! Kuraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.87,0:25:11.10,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.84,0:25:19.55,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.55,0:25:22.35,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Moi's important jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.35,0:25:25.41,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That it was used on a brat like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:38.70,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.41,0:25:48.34,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kuraiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.94,0:25:51.21,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't able to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.47,0:26:22.77,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuraiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.15,0:26:28.91,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Sid, it seems that I did become an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.96,0:26:41.76,Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:04.52,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.52,0:27:07.85,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The dream of one day
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.85,0:27:11.16,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Is not your imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.16,0:27:15.63,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe that you can do it
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.63,0:27:17.86,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.86,0:27:21.30,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We're under the same sky
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.30,0:27:24.60,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm watching you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.60,0:27:28.87,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel my presence
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.05,0:27:40.25,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,When you start running
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.25,0:27:43.79,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,The winds of fate will change
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.79,0:27:45.96,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little sad
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.96,0:27:50.03,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Because yesterday gets farther away
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:52.63,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.63,0:27:56.87,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind up the unraveling threads
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.87,0:27:58.77,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.17,0:28:02.91,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put your heart into it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.91,0:28:06.11,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go where you want
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.11,0:28:08.45,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.45,0:28:11.82,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.82,0:28:15.19,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Show your imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.19,0:28:19.56,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your shining eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.56,0:28:21.93,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.93,0:28:25.30,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In any circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.30,0:28:28.64,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,That I am watching you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.64,0:28:32.97,Ending Song,,0000,0000,0000,,That I am here for you